msgid "stone knives and bearskins"
msgstr "stone knives and bearskins"

#: ../../S/stone-knives-and-bearskins.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../S/stone-knives-and-bearskins.rst:9
msgid ""
"[from the Star Trek Classic episode *The City on the Edge of Forever*\\] A "
"term traditionally used to describe (and deprecate) computing environments "
"that are grotesquely primitive in light of what is known about good ways to "
"design things. As in \"Don't get too used to the facilities here. Once you "
"leave SAIL it's stone knives and bearskins as far as the eye can see\". "
"Compare :ref:`steam-powered`\\."
msgstr ""
"[Star Trekのクラシックエピソード\\ *The City on the Edge of Forever*\\ から] "
"物事をうまく設計する方法について知られていることに照らして、ぞっとするほど原始的なコンピューティング環境を表す(そしてけなす)ために伝統的に使われる用語。「ここの設備にあまり慣れるな。いったんSAILを離れれば、見渡す限りstone"
" knives and bearskinsだ」のように。\\ :ref:`steam-powered`\\ と比較せよ。"
